Schnittstelle UserStringConstants

Alle bekannten Unterschnittstellen:
GUIConstants
Alle bekannten Implementierungsklassen:
AnswerRowPanel, AnswersPanel, MessagePanel, MyButtonPanel, QFrame, QuestionButtonPanel, QuestionListPanel, QuestionMetaPanel, QuestionPanel, QuizButtonPanel, QuizInfoViewPanel, QuizMainPanel, QuizQuestionMainPanel, QuizThemeMainPanel, TabPane, ThemeButtonPanel, ThemeHeaderPanel, ThemeListPanel, ThemePanel
public interface UserStringConstants
Central constants for all user-displayed strings in the quiz application. This interface contains all German text labels, button texts, messages, and other strings that are visible to the end user.
Seit:
1.0
Version:
1.0
Autor:
Christos Poulios
